{"title":"凯旋忆当年（三）","authors":["西虹","西野"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":22}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"凯旋忆当年（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"西虹词  西野画"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就因这事心发恨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我跟地主来顶嘴；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饿狼咬猪人难防，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为何叫我来包赔。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"地主狗脸不认人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开言骂我小杂种，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养猪还能杀肉吃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你有什么了不起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我的小猪虽不大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过年就是百多斤；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这样算法便宜你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不然老账算不清。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骂着叫着威风大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老粗木棒手中拿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咬牙瞪眼奔我来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身上下打不停。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"木棒起处鲜血流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青伤紫血染衣红；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喊天哭地谁来理？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昏昏沉沉倒下身。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"醒来时左腿糊上血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一拖一爬转家中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在家养伤整两月，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又流血又流脓。    （附图片）"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}